window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Inside the Game, players struggle to survive in a world where technology no longer functions. </p> <p>On Tygon, fans are unable to view what is occurring inside the Game. </p> <p>Trew and Danielle rush to save both realities, but they are unable to know what the other is doing. The fate of reality depends on a Game, and time is about to run out.... </p>"; 
